I had to do something with a ziploc full of leftover mussels, so I made them into this soup. I used fewer mussels than called for, more cream (about 1/2c) and added 4 small diced potatoes. Really yummy! (It should be noted that I didn't actually *eat* any of the mussels, but the soup they were in was quite satisfying.)

